extracted_information: Finnhub.io provides APIs for economic data, including an Economic Calendar, Economic Codes, and Economic Data. The Economic Calendar API offers recent and upcoming economic releases.

features: Access to recent and upcoming economic releases.
Ability to filter economic calendar by date range.
Identification of economic indicators through codes.
Retrieval of historical economic data points by code.
